http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Cab-driver-murdered/article14617786.ece

A 34-year-old cab driver was found murdered at the temple premises in Rajanukunte in the outskirts of the city on Thursday.Harish, a resident of Bagaluru, went for night shift and later found murdered at the temple premises.Harish body was found tied to an electric pole with the help of a banner cloth. He was strangulated to death.Harish was married eight years ago and had no children. The Rajanukunte police have registered a case and investigations are on.